fields.question:
I might be your enemy or your friend. I am always around you. You have two choices: either trust or dubiety.

Every time you move around I come closer to my victory. Guessing me isn't easy I planned your assassination not it's your turn to plan mine. If you guessed me right deduce my role from where I come. That will lead to my termination

1) But this time you have no option but to set yourself free from confinement. I already have the controls and you have limited time to revitalize. Did you guess me yet?? I am sure not.

2) Is it still difficult?? Okay so just put on the code or mark the finger impression that can lead you to my end !! That was a help to you. Now your turn comes to be the Terminator. Grab your chance, follow the next step until you unlock the next can't go back to the initiator.

3) Ohh you survived !!!! Well here's the final hint I am the mask that can bring you fortune or misery. The choice is yours, choose me as a fortune or as a misery, might get benefitted either. Run back to the first one as I give you the last chance to destroy me or let me win over you.

Hint 3:
If the sign is between two tiles on the same row:
1. The + sign means the tile on the right will be [number on left] +1.
2. The - sign means the tile on the right will be [number on left] -1.

If the sign is between two tiles on the same column:
1. The + sign means the tile on the bottom will be [number on top] +1.
2. The - sign means the tile on the bottom will be [number on top] -1.

Each row will have number from 1 to 7, similar to sudoku.
Each column will have number from 1 to 7, similar to sudoku.

Hint 4: After filling 4th row correctly, 7th row becomes key or important.
